The implementation references the public design ideas of QiaoKes/fntv-electron:
https://github.com/QiaoKes/fntv-electron

This repository does not vendor Android SDK, Gradle, JDK, emulator system images,
release signing keys, APK artifacts, or private service credentials. Local tools
and generated files are kept out of source control through .gitignore.

Playback compatibility uses IJKPlayer:
https://github.com/bilibili/ijkplayer
IJKPlayer is distributed under LGPL-2.1 and includes FFmpeg-based native
playback components. Binary redistribution must preserve the corresponding
third-party license notices.

Playback compatibility also uses VLC for Android / LibVLC:
https://github.com/videolan/vlc-android
LibVLC is distributed under LGPL-2.1 or later. Binary redistribution must
preserve the corresponding VLC/LibVLC license notices and allow recipients to
exercise LGPL rights for the linked native playback components.
